column5: GREAT PLACE IF YOU'RE IN TOWN FOR SXSW!!! 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath located in West Campus Neighborhood, can sleep up to 6. Has Kitchen, clean towels, clean linens, 2 parking spots! Wifi, hot water, pet friendly! 5 minute ride to Downtown Austin for SXSW events, great base camp for your time in Austin!
column8: Perfect place to stay if you're in town for SXSW
